ck listing\n| collapsed       = yes\n| headline        = 1981 US and Canada edition\n| total_length    = 47:58\n| title1          = Another One Bites the Dust\n| length1         = 3:37\n| title2          = Bohemian Rhapsody\n| length2         = 5:58\n| title3          = Crazy Little Thing Called Love\n| length3         = 2:44\n| title4          = Killer Queen\n| length4         = 3:02\n| title5          = Fat Bottomed Girls\n| length5         = 3:23\n| title6          = Bicycle Race\n| length6         = 3:01\n| title7          = [[Under Pressure]]\n| note7           = later included on ''[[Hot Space]]'', 1982\n| writer7         = Queen, [[David Bowie]]\n| length7         = 4:05\n| title8          = We Will Rock You\n| length8         = 2:02\n| title9          = We Are the Champions\n| length9         = 3:01\n| title10         = Flash\n| length10        = 2:49\n| title11         = Somebody to Love\n| length11        = 4:58\n| title12         = You're My Best Friend\n| length12        = 2:52\n| title13         = [[Keep Yourself Alive]]\n| note13          = single version in mono, from ''[[Queen (Queen album)|Queen]]'', 1973\n| writer13        = May\n| length13        = 3:32\n| title14         = Play the Game\n| length14        = 3:30\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed       = yes\n| headline        = 1981 Japan edition\n| total_length    = 60:37\n| title1          = Bohemian Rhapsody\n| length1         = 5:55\n| title2          = Another One Bites the Dust\n| length2         = 3:33\n| title3          = Killer Queen\n| length3         = 3:00\n| title4          = Fat Bottomed Girls\n| length4         = 3:22\n| title5          = Good Old-Fashioned Lover Boy\n| length5         = 2:32\n| title6          = Don't Stop Me Now\n| length6         = 3:28\n| title7          = Save Me\n| length7         = 3:48\n| title8          = Under Pressure\n| length8         = 4:05\n| title9          = Crazy Little Thing Called Love\n| length9         = 2:42\n| title10         = Somebody to